The greatest fear that humans have is not the fear of "death" but the fear of "living" e.i living their true lives. We are often so concerned about pleasing others that we never really reveal our true selves because we are afraid of being judged or being the outcasts; so we ended up living in fear. To live a fear free life you need to start taking what people think about you "not" personally because whatever a person may think of you is as a result of what he/she has been taught growing up, they have a false belief about you because they don't know you. You were raised in different families with different beliefs/values, so how could they be right about you?. Don't take things personally and you will live a fearless life. #fearless @thefouragreement . @the_four_agreements_official @the_four_agreements .
